data.description: Welcome to your Florida dream pool home with boating access! This charming single-family pool home, nestled on almost half an acre, offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. This property boasts three bedrooms, two bathrooms with a new roof in 2022. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space, and a breakfast bar for casual dining. There is room for potential expansion with almost 1/2 acre. A deeded boat slip with water access is great for boating enthusiasts that is minutes away from open waters with no bridges to navigate. The property includes a convenient storage or she shed for all your extra space. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this fantastic single-family pool home with deeded boat slip in Palm Shores Punta Gorda.
